	<part id="part-installation-ibm-power">
		<title>IBM Power&nbsp;Systems - Installation and Booting</title>
		<partintro>
			<para>
				This part of the <citetitle>&PRODUCT; Installation Guide</citetitle> includes information about installation and basic post-installation troubleshooting for IBM Power&nbsp;Systems servers. IBM Power&nbsp;Systems servers include IBM PowerLinux servers and POWER7 and POWER8 Power&nbsp;Systems servers running Linux. For advanced installation options, see <xref linkend="part-advanced-installation-options" />.
			</para>
			<important>
				<para>
					Previous releases of &PRODUCT; supported 32-bit and 64-bit Power&nbsp;Systems servers (<literal>ppc</literal> and <literal>ppc64</literal>, respectively). &PRODUCT;&nbsp;7 supports only 64-bit Power&nbsp;Systems servers (<literal>ppc64</literal>).
				</para>
			</important>
		</partintro>
